flowRoot.flowPara: Anna is a mother of two children, 9 and 11 years old, married to Bruce for the last 15 years.Bruce works as nurse in the same hospital as Anna. Lately his sugar level got a bit higher and he needs to lower the sugar and alcohol consumption. Bruce love wine, and he used to drink at List one glass a night. Anna is trying to take care of him and balance his alcohol consumption and started to cook Low sugar dishes. They live in a suburb next to NYC.Possible Scenario:Anna uses the App to help her husband to monitor and observed how much alcohol he is consuming
